handleFirstCfp

public abstract jade.lang.acl.ACLMessage handleFirstCfp(jade.lang.acl.ACLMessage cfp)
Handles a CFP message. This method is invoked when the first CFP is received, and is supposed to create the reply to be sent: either a PROPOSE (with a Proposal as content) or a REFUSE.

handleCfpWithFeedback

public abstract jade.lang.acl.ACLMessage handleCfpWithFeedback(jade.lang.acl.ACLMessage newCFP)
Handles a CFP message. This method is invoked when a CFP with feedback is received (from the second negotiation round onwards), and is supposed to create the reply to be sent: either a PROPOSE (with a Proposal as content) or a REFUSE.
